job.title: .NET Developer

customFields.generatedDescriptionAI:
We are looking for a talented and experienced .NET Developer to join our team. This is a long-term project, with a duration of more than 6 months. 

As a .NET Developer, you will be responsible for developing and maintaining our web applications using .NET Core, .NET Framework, and ASP.NET. You will also be working with Microsoft SQL Server to design and optimize database structures. 

Key skills for this role include proficiency in C#, JavaScript, jQuery, and ASP.NET MVC. You should have a strong understanding of API development and integration. 

To qualify for this position, please submit a proposal detailing how you can contribute to this project. Additionally, include links to your past completed projects that showcase your expertise in .NET development. We look forward to reviewing your proposal and discussing further details with you.
